Paper: hep-th/9907218

Date: 1999-07-29

Title: Deformed oscillators algebra formulation of the Nonlinear Schrodinger

hierarchy and of its symmetryAuthors: E. Ragoucy

Comments: Proceedings of QGIS-99, Prague, June 17-19 1999, 7 pages

Journal-ref: Czech.J.Phys. 50 (2000) 163-168

We present a self-contained formulation of the Nonlinear Schrodingerhierarchy and its Yangian symmetry in terms of deformed oscilator algebra (Z.F.algebra). The link between Yangian Y(gl(N)) and finite W(gl(pN),N.gl(p))algebras is also illustrated in this framework.